      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age and will need some upcoming maintenance. While the engine and transmission are functional, you may notice some minor fluid seepage and occasional suspension noise over bumps. The exterior has several scratches and some fading paint, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who is willing to invest in some minor repairs and detailing to bring it back to its best.",
