      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain is crisp, and the VANOS system has been professionally serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains tight, with the rear subframe already reinforced to mitigate common fatigue issues. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are razor-sharp, making it a perfect candidate for the purist who values visceral feedback over a museum-piece finish.",
